(16036, 10944, 0, 5, '面具', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0000, 30, 0, 7, '面具                                  詞 Caroline 曲/Arrangement: Kevin \r\n什麼時候 才能逃離 這種生活 \r\n卻總是披著面具度過\r\n想要解脫 掙扎的心又帶點懦弱\r\n空虛的我 在邊緣遊走\r\n\r\n沉溺在時間的黑洞之中\r\n想遠遠逃離這個虛偽的牢籠\r\n空虛的幻想自己漂流隨風\r\n現實的包袱卻變的越來越沉重\r\n\r\n算了吧 就這樣吧  我早已看透這世界的虛假\r\n錯了嗎 我變了嗎  理想的世界不過是童話\r\n算了吧 就這樣吧  面具裡的你是什麼模樣\r\n錯了嗎 我變了嗎   只是我已經懶的去想像\r\n\r\n看過了多少相同的劇情  \r\n相同的結局 (太多的打擊)\r\n看到了多少人為了現實而放棄\r\n曾經有過追逐夢想的 勇氣 \r\n \r\n決定不再讓自己去承受\r\n我要解脫這束縛的枷鎖\r\n讓時間盡情的放縱  \r\n我要翱翔在天空\r\n就當作這個世界遺棄了我 \r\n', '', 257, '', '嘉文', '筱蓉 嘉文', '嘉文', '魔弦音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-03-05 04:47:11', '2013-10-07 17:14:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16037, 10944, 0, 6, '你說過', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0000, 30, 0, 1, '  詞曲:Caroline 編曲Kevin\r\n\r\n你說過 你說過 要帶著我環遊世界\r\n你說過 會與我共度每一天\r\n\r\n你愛我 對你撒嬌的那一面\r\n你卻不知道 我喜歡你的哪一點\r\n\r\n你說過 願意追隨我到天邊\r\n你也說 天塌了你會在我身邊\r\n\r\n你愛我  總是對你笑的很甜\r\n你卻沒說 其實我並沒有在你心裡面\r\n\r\n就讓那些美好的謊言(誓言) 化成雲煙(一一幻滅)\r\n你也不必感到抱歉 就當我們不曾永有這一切\r\n\r\n讓風帶著我去尋找 新的力量 新的方向\r\n我將會看見 最真實的 屬於自己的模樣\r\n\r\n已被撕裂的心 一片一片掉落在地面上\r\n臉頰上灼熱的淚 一滴一滴消失再 曾經屬於我們的地方\r\n', '', 307, '', 'kevin carol', 'carol', 'kevin', '魔弦音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-03-05 04:49:13', '2013-10-07 17:14:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16038, 10944, 0, 7, 'Born to stand out', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0000, 30, 0, 5, 'Born to Stand Out\r\n\r\n\r\nI can’t tell the way I feel about you\r\nBut I know there is something unusual\r\n(Somehow)\r\nI feel like knowing you for long time\r\nAnd you certainly got the qualities \r\nmade you the way you are \r\nI don’t have a word for you to describe now\r\nAnd you’re making me feel really special\r\nAnd you’re like a magnet \r\nCatch me from the first sight\r\nBaby I am going crazy I’ll do anything to see you smile\r\nThere is magic surround you A\r\nI can’t resist your charm  #Cm\r\nEvery time you look me in the eye   D\r\nAlmost feel like flying high \r\n\r\nLittle things you do it makes me happy \r\nThe L word you know it makes me crazy\r\nYou don’t need no fancy cars \r\n‘Cause you are born to stand out \r\nI like the way you whisper in my ear\r\nSaying you’ll always be here\r\nJust the way you are \r\nBorn to stand out \r\n\r\nCHORDS: \r\n\r\n\r\n‘Cause you are born to stand out\r\nYou don’t need no fancy clothes\r\nBorn to stand out \r\nYou’re meant to be in the spotlights \r\n', '', 264, '', 'carol', 'carol', 'kevin', '魔弦音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-03-05 04:51:07', '2013-10-07 17:14:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16039, 10944, 1743, 1, 'FEVER', '', '2008-01-01 00:00:00', 0000, 30, 0, 1, 'Fever\r\n歌詞 CAROL 曲:KEVIN KUO 編曲 嘉文\r\nIs it so called chaos?\r\nIt’s like you have become my alcohol \r\nI am so addicted\r\nAnd I don’t wanna be sober / don’t wanna be sober at daytime\r\nYou are like the only thing \r\nThat I can’t resist\r\nYou are like the illness \r\nThat never gonna be cured\r\n\r\nYour touch satisfies me\r\nYour lips they taste so sweet\r\nEach cell of me is longing for you\r\nSo many times I tried to quit \r\nBut never have I succeed \r\nI’m helplessly falling into you\r\n\r\nIt’s a fever, fever\r\nWhen we’re having eye contact \r\nIt’s a fever, fever\r\nWhen I have you in mind \r\nMy blood goes hot\r\nEach time your fingertip slide down my arm\r\n\r\nIt’s a fever\r\nI cannot control my heartbeat\r\nIt’s like taking drugs\r\nYou’re making me high \r\n', '', 258, '', '筱蓉', '筱蓉', '嘉文', '魔弦音樂', '', 0, 1, 0, '2009-03-05 07:46:44', '2015-03-12 13:38:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
